---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="院内設備"
  description="久下耳鼻咽喉科の最新医療機器をご紹介します。"
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="pt-9 pb-5 bg-white text-primary-800">
    <div class="container-max">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-normal mb-2 bg-primary-700 text-white p-4 rounded-md">院内設備</h1>
      <p class="text-base  text-primary-800">
        最新の医療機器で、正確な診断と質の高い治療をお約束します。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white pt-1">
    <div class="container-max max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-6 mt-0">待合室</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
          <img
            src="/images/facilities0001.jpg"
            alt="待合室"
            width="303"
            height="227"
            class="h-full object-contain"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
          <img
            src="/images/facilities0003.jpg"
            alt="待合室"
            width="146"
            height="226"
            class="h-full object-contain"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
          <img
            src="/images/facilities0004.jpg"
            alt="待合室"
            width="144"
            height="224"
            class="h-full object-contain"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
          <img
            src="/images/facilities0002.jpg"
            alt="待合室"
            width="301"
            height="226"
            class="h-full object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-12">
        待合室はゆったりしたスペースをご用意しております。トイレは、バリアフリーで車イス、ベビーカーに対応しています。
        また、サイドコーナーではお子様用DVDを放映しております。
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-6 mt-0">診察室</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0005.jpg"
              alt="診察室"
              width="303"
              height="227"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <p>電子カルテ、画像ファイリング使用</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0006.jpg"
              alt="診察室"
              width="301"
              height="226"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0007.jpg"
              alt="採血・点滴コーナー"
              width="303"
              height="227"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <p>採血・点滴コーナー</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0008.jpg"
              alt="聴力・鼓膜検査機器"
              width="301"
              height="226"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <p>聴力・鼓膜検査機器</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0009.jpg"
              alt="聴力・鼓膜検査機器"
              width="146"
              height="226"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0010.jpg"
              alt="レントゲンCR装置"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <p>レントゲンCR装置</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0011.jpg"
              alt="ネブライザー吸入材器"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <p>ネブライザー吸入材器</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
            <img
              src="/images/facilities0012.jpg"
              alt="電子スコープほか"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <p>電子スコープほか</p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
